### Tech Stack

|Layer          |Technology                                   |Why                                                      |
|---------------|---------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------|
|Backend        |FastAPI (existing)                           |Already built. Async-native, fast.                       |
|Frontend       |React + Vite + TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui       |Fast dev, good components, dark mode                     |
|Database       |PostgreSQL + SQLAlchemy + Alembic            |Relational data, migrations, JSONB for flexible fields   |
|Cache/Queue    |Redis                                        |Job queue, rate limiting, caching, real-time pub/sub     |
|Background Jobs|Celery + Redis broker                        |Scraping jobs, scheduled emails, AI processing           |
|AI             |Claude API (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)        |Message personalization, lead scoring, company research  |
|Email          |Resend API (or Amazon SES)                   |Transactional + outreach emails, open/click tracking     |
|Scraping       |Playwright (existing) + httpx + BeautifulSoup|Headless browser for JS-heavy sites, lightweight for APIs|
|File Storage   |Local / MinIO (S3-compatible)                |Attachments, exports, portfolio files                    |
|Deployment     |Docker Compose → VPS (Hetzner $10/mo)        |Cheap, full control, EU/US options                       |
|Auth           |JWT + OAuth2 (FastAPI built-in)              |Single user, but future-proof for team                   |

