## 7. DEPLOYMENT

```yaml
# docker-compose.yml
services:
  api:
    build: ./backend
    ports: ["8000:8000"]
    depends_on: [db, redis]
    env_file: .env

  frontend:
    build: ./frontend
    ports: ["3000:3000"]

  db:
    image: postgres:16
    volumes: ["pgdata:/var/lib/postgresql/data"]
    env_file: .env

  redis:
    image: redis:7-alpine
    ports: ["6379:6379"]

  celery_worker:
    build: ./backend
    command: celery -A app.celery worker -l info
    depends_on: [redis, db]

  celery_beat:
    build: ./backend
    command: celery -A app.celery beat -l info
    depends_on: [redis]

volumes:
  pgdata:
```

**Production**: Hetzner CX31 (4 vCPU, 8GB RAM, 80GB SSD) — €8.39/month. More than enough for single-user app with background workers.

